Description: Provides GIS and map utilities, plus additional modeling
        tools for developing cellular automata, dynamic raster models,
        and agent based models in 'SpaDES'.  Included are various
        methods for spatial spreading, spatial agents, GIS operations,
        random map generation, and others.  See '?SpaDES.tools' for an
        categorized overview of these additional tools.  The suggested
        package 'NLMR' can be installed from the following repository:
        (<https://PredictiveEcology.r-universe.dev>).
